COMPONENT NAME: RKM Netezza
AUTHOR: Oracle
DESCRIPTION: - Reverse Knowledge Module - Reverse engineering Knowledge Module to retrieve the tables, and views from a Netezza database.
RESTRICTIONS: - The mask of tables to reverse must not be empty, and at least contain the '%' character. - The tab Selective reverse cannot be used with this knowledge module.

insert into SNP_REV_KEY ( MOD_GUID, TABLE_NAME, KEY_NAME, CONS_TYPE, IND_ACTIVE, CHECK_FLOW, CHECK_STAT ) Values ( '<%=odiRef.getModel("GLOBAL_ID")%>', :TABLE_NAME, :KEY_NAME, :CONS_TYPE, '1', '1', '1' )

select distinct relation as TABLE_NAME, 'PK' as CONS_TYPE, constraintname as KEY_NAME from _v_relation_keydata where contype = 'p' and database = '<%=odiRef.getModel("CATALOG_NAME")%>' and owner = '<%=odiRef.getModel("SCHEMA_NAME")%>' and relation like '<%=odiRef.getModel("REV_OBJ_PATT")%>' and '<%=odiRef.getModel("REV_OBJ_TYPE")%>' like '%T%'
insert into SNP_REV_KEY_COL ( MOD_GUID, TABLE_NAME, KEY_NAME, COL_NAME, POS ) Values ( '<%=odiRef.getModel("GLOBAL_ID")%>', :TABLE_NAME, :KEY_NAME, :COL_NAME, :POS )

select relation as TABLE_NAME, constraintname as KEY_NAME, conseq as POS, attname as COL_NAME from _v_relation_keydata where contype = 'p' and database = '<%=odiRef.getModel("CATALOG_NAME")%>' and owner = '<%=odiRef.getModel("SCHEMA_NAME")%>' and relation like '<%=odiRef.getModel("REV_OBJ_PATT")%>' and '<%=odiRef.getModel("REV_OBJ_TYPE")%>' like '%T%'

insert into SNP_REV_KEY ( MOD_GUID, TABLE_NAME, KEY_NAME, CONS_TYPE, IND_ACTIVE, CHECK_FLOW, CHECK_STAT ) Values ( '<%=odiRef.getModel("GLOBAL_ID")%>', :TABLE_NAME, :KEY_NAME, :CONS_TYPE, '1', '1', '1' )

select distinct relation as TABLE_NAME, 'AK' as CONS_TYPE, constraintname as KEY_NAME from _v_relation_keydata where contype = 'u' and database = '<%=odiRef.getModel("CATALOG_NAME")%>' and owner = '<%=odiRef.getModel("SCHEMA_NAME")%>' and relation like '<%=odiRef.getModel("REV_OBJ_PATT")%>' and '<%=odiRef.getModel("REV_OBJ_TYPE")%>' like '%T%'
insert into SNP_REV_KEY_COL ( MOD_GUID, TABLE_NAME, KEY_NAME, COL_NAME, POS ) Values ( '<%=odiRef.getModel("GLOBAL_ID")%>', :TABLE_NAME, :KEY_NAME, :COL_NAME, :POS )

select relation as TABLE_NAME, constraintname as KEY_NAME, conseq as POS, attname as COL_NAME from _v_relation_keydata where contype = 'u' and database = '<%=odiRef.getModel("CATALOG_NAME")%>' and owner = '<%=odiRef.getModel("SCHEMA_NAME")%>' and relation like '<%=odiRef.getModel("REV_OBJ_PATT")%>' and '<%=odiRef.getModel("REV_OBJ_TYPE")%>' like '%T%'

insert into SNP_REV_COL ( MOD_GUID, TABLE_NAME, COL_NAME, DT_DRIVER, COL_HEADING, COL_DESC_C, POS, LONGC, SCALEC, COL_MANDATORY, CHECK_STAT, CHECK_FLOW ) values ( '<%=odiRef.getModel("GLOBAL_ID")%>', :TABLE_NAME, :COL_NAME, :DT_DRIVER, :COL_HEADING, :COL_DESC, :POS, :LONGC, :SCALEC, :COL_MANDATORY, '1', '1' )

select C.name as TABLE_NAME, C.attname as COL_NAME, FORMAT_SQL_TYPE(C.ATTTYPID) as DT_DRIVER, C.attname as COL_HEADING, C.description as COL_DESC, C.attnum as POS, case when FORMAT_SQL_TYPE(C.ATTTYPID)='TIMESTAMP' then FORMAT_SCALE(C.ATTTYPID, C.ATTTYPMOD) else FORMAT_PREC(C.ATTTYPID, C.ATTTYPMOD, INT4(C.ATTLEN)) end as LONGC, case when FORMAT_SQL_TYPE(C.ATTTYPID)='TIMESTAMP' then FORMAT_PREC(C.ATTTYPID, C.ATTTYPMOD, INT4(C.ATTLEN)) else FORMAT_SCALE(C.ATTTYPID, C.ATTTYPMOD) end as SCALEC, case when C.attnotnull = 'true' then '1' else '0' end as COL_MANDATORY from _v_relation_column C where C.database = '<%=odiRef.getModel("CATALOG_NAME")%>' and C.owner = '<%=odiRef.getModel("SCHEMA_NAME")%>' and C.name like '<%=odiRef.getModel("REV_OBJ_PATT")%>' and C.type like '%TABLE%' and '<%=odiRef.getModel("REV_OBJ_TYPE")%>' like '%T%'

insert into SNP_REV_TABLE ( MOD_GUID, TABLE_NAME, RES_NAME, TABLE_ALIAS, TABLE_TYPE, TABLE_DESC_C, IND_SHOW ) values ( '<%=odiRef.getModel("GLOBAL_ID")%>', :TABLE_NAME, :RES_NAME, :TABLE_ALIAS, :TABLE_TYPE, :TABLE_DESC, '1' )

select T.tablename as TABLE_NAME, T.tablename as RES_NAME, case when T.tablename like '<%=odiRef.getModel("REV_ALIAS_LTRIM")%>%' and '<%=odiRef.getModel("REV_ALIAS_LTRIM")%>%' != '%' then substr(T.tablename, length('<%=odiRef.getModel("REV_ALIAS_LTRIM")%>')+1, length(T.tablename)) else T.tablename end as TABLE_ALIAS, T.description as TABLE_DESC, 'T' as TABLE_TYPE from _v_table as T, _v_objs_owned as OO where OO.database = '<%=odiRef.getModel("CATALOG_NAME")%>' and T.owner = '<%=odiRef.getModel("SCHEMA_NAME")%>' and OO.OBJID = T.OBJID and T.tablename like '<%=odiRef.getModel("REV_OBJ_PATT")%>' and '<%=odiRef.getModel("REV_OBJ_TYPE")%>' like '%T%'

insert into SNP_REV_COL ( MOD_GUID, TABLE_NAME, COL_NAME, DT_DRIVER, COL_HEADING, COL_DESC_C, POS, LONGC, SCALEC, COL_MANDATORY, CHECK_STAT, CHECK_FLOW ) values ( '<%=odiRef.getModel("GLOBAL_ID")%>', :TABLE_NAME, :COL_NAME, :DT_DRIVER, :COL_HEADING, :COL_DESC, :POS, :LONGC, :SCALEC, :COL_MANDATORY, '1', '1' )

select C.name as TABLE_NAME, C.attname as COL_NAME, FORMAT_SQL_TYPE(C.ATTTYPID) as DT_DRIVER, C.attname as COL_HEADING, C.description as COL_DESC, C.attnum as POS, case when FORMAT_SQL_TYPE(C.ATTTYPID)='TIMESTAMP' then FORMAT_SCALE(C.ATTTYPID, C.ATTTYPMOD) else FORMAT_PREC(C.ATTTYPID, C.ATTTYPMOD, INT4(C.ATTLEN)) end as LONGC, case when FORMAT_SQL_TYPE(C.ATTTYPID)='TIMESTAMP' then FORMAT_PREC(C.ATTTYPID, C.ATTTYPMOD, INT4(C.ATTLEN)) else FORMAT_SCALE(C.ATTTYPID, C.ATTTYPMOD) end as SCALEC, case when C.attnotnull = 'true' then '1' else '0' end as COL_MANDATORY from _v_relation_column C where C.database = '<%=odiRef.getModel("CATALOG_NAME")%>' and C.owner = '<%=odiRef.getModel("SCHEMA_NAME")%>' and C.name like '<%=odiRef.getModel("REV_OBJ_PATT")%>' and C.type like '%VIEW%' and '<%=odiRef.getModel("REV_OBJ_TYPE")%>' like '%V%'

insert into SNP_REV_TABLE ( MOD_GUID, TABLE_NAME, RES_NAME, TABLE_ALIAS, TABLE_TYPE, TABLE_DESC_C, IND_SHOW ) values ( '<%=odiRef.getModel("GLOBAL_ID")%>', :TABLE_NAME, :RES_NAME, :TABLE_ALIAS, :TABLE_TYPE, :TABLE_DESC, '1' )

select T.viewname as TABLE_NAME, T.viewname as RES_NAME, case when T.viewname like '<%=odiRef.getModel("REV_ALIAS_LTRIM")%>%' and '<%=odiRef.getModel("REV_ALIAS_LTRIM")%>%' != '%' then substr(T.viewname, length('<%=odiRef.getModel("REV_ALIAS_LTRIM")%>')+1, length(T.viewname)) else T.viewname end as TABLE_ALIAS, T.description as TABLE_DESC, 'V' as TABLE_TYPE from _v_view as T, _v_objs_owned as OO where OO.database = '<%=odiRef.getModel("CATALOG_NAME")%>' and T.owner = '<%=odiRef.getModel("SCHEMA_NAME")%>' and OO.OBJID = T.OBJID and T.viewname like '<%=odiRef.getModel("REV_OBJ_PATT")%>' and '<%=odiRef.getModel("REV_OBJ_TYPE")%>' like '%V%'

insert into SNP_REV_JOIN ( MOD_GUID, FK_NAME, TABLE_NAME, FK_TYPE, PK_CATALOG, PK_SCHEMA, PK_TABLE_NAME, CHECK_STAT, CHECK_FLOW, IND_ACTIVE ) values ( '<%=odiRef.getModel("GLOBAL_ID")%>', :FK_NAME, :TABLE_NAME, 'D', :PK_CATALOG, :PK_SCHEMA, :PK_TABLE_NAME, '1', '1', '1' )

select distinct relation as TABLE_NAME, constraintname as FK_NAME, pkdatabase as PK_CATALOG, pkowner as PK_SCHEMA, pkrelation as PK_TABLE_NAME from _v_relation_keydata where contype = 'f' and database = '<%=odiRef.getModel("CATALOG_NAME")%>' and owner = '<%=odiRef.getModel("SCHEMA_NAME")%>' and relation like '<%=odiRef.getModel("REV_OBJ_PATT")%>' and '<%=odiRef.getModel("REV_OBJ_TYPE")%>' like '%T%'

insert into SNP_REV_JOIN_COL ( MOD_GUID, FK_NAME, FK_COL_NAME, FK_TABLE_NAME, PK_COL_NAME, PK_TABLE_NAME, POS ) Values ( '<%=odiRef.getModel("GLOBAL_ID")%>', :FK_NAME, :FK_COL_NAME, :FK_TABLE_NAME, :PK_COL_NAME, :PK_TABLE_NAME, :POS )

select relation as FK_TABLE_NAME, pkrelation as PK_TABLE_NAME, constraintname as FK_NAME, attname as FK_COL_NAME, pkattname as PK_COL_NAME, conseq as POS from _v_relation_keydata where contype = 'f' and database = '<%=odiRef.getModel("CATALOG_NAME")%>' and owner = '<%=odiRef.getModel("SCHEMA_NAME")%>' and relation like '<%=odiRef.getModel("REV_OBJ_PATT")%>' and '<%=odiRef.getModel("REV_OBJ_TYPE")%>' like '%T%'
